message:
{{#is_alert}}

Critical Alarm Detected on Nutanix Cluster `{{ntnx_cluster_name}}`

A critical system alarm has been detected and repeated within the last 5 minutes.  
Manual resolution is required in Nutanix Prism to stop recurrence.

This alert will automatically resolve in Datadog if it disappears for more than 5 minutes.
To resolve immediately, mark it as Resolved directly in Prism.

{{/is_alert}}

{{#is_recovery}}

Nutanix Alarm Resolved in Cluster `{{ntnx_cluster_name}}`

The following critical alarm has not been seen for more than 5 minutes and is now considered resolved:

Cluster status is back to normal. Good job!

{{/is_recovery}}
